    "Information"
    ,
    
    "consequences" : [
    
    
    
    "Bond the retainer plate at an ambient temperature of between 20 and 25 °C."
    ,
    
    
    "The material temperature must be maintained so that there are no dew-point differences (condensation). "
    
    ]
