    "category" :
    
    
    "Information"
    ,
    
    "consequences" : [
    
    
    
    "Adhesive must be applied using the EPX application system developed by 3M."
    ,
    
    
    "The original mixing nozzles must be used."
    ,
    
    
    "If the mixing nozzle is left on the cartridge for longer than the processing time of 2-3 minutes, it must be replaced with a new nozzle."
    ,
    
    
    "Adhesive must be applied in such a way that the bead of adhesive is pressed in by approx. 50 % at the joint. This is necessary in order to achieve adequate contact/coating."
    ,
    
    
    "The retainer plate must be affixed within the processing time of 2-3 minutes."
    
    ]
