    "The final bonding strength is achieved after approx. 24 hours at room temperature. No pressure should be applied to the bonded area during this time."
    ,
    
    
    "The final bonding strength is achieved after only about 30 minutes when stored at approx. 70 °C. No pressure should be applied to the bonded area during this time."
    
